snippet.title: IS AMBER HEARD EMPOWERED? OR IS SHE DELUSIONAL?
snippet.description:
Look at that nameless person being so empowered that she actually lifts weights while holding her baby.

Not making fun of alcoholic women who are sick but rather of narcissistic abusers who manipulate, lie, gaslight, and use violence to control others. Regardless of their sex these people need to be called out.

#amberheard is delusional and needs to be held accountable for her violence against others. Not rewarded for it. #jeez #getagrip
Thanks 

#amberheard #johnnydepp #narcissiticabuse
